{"id": 1366, "genre": 1000, "title": "【好奇心x豌豆荚】在APP的使用习惯上，你更接近哪一型人格？", "description": "我是“16G手机肯定不够用”型。（题图来自：豌豆荚）", "record_count": 31868, "comment_count": 49, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161215150510N71XdVMR9rIoZv4F.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-12-19T17:00:38Z", "questions": [{"id": 1461, "title": "【好奇心x豌豆荚】在APP的使用习惯上，你更接近哪一型人格？", "content": "【好奇心x豌豆荚】你是哪一型 App 使用者？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 140555, "content": "囤积癖，下载之后再也没打开过的 App 超过 10 个", "image": "img/option/option/20161215114525FLTGWnobBY0zlrgs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 140564, "content": "研究比较型，把同类型的App全部下载，比较后留下好用的", "image": "img/option/option/20161215114513RkxFmEzhyCiqWuvJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 140573, "content": "分类强迫症，坚持自己独特的分类方式，比如按首字母", "image": "img/option/option/20161220131412LJP9DI6qVl4kQZ78.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 140574, "content": "颜控，挑选App的依据一般是图标和界面的样子", "image": "img/option/option/20161215114411dZEoBHltD0uS6GVF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 140578, "content": "探索型，打开应用商店之后一定会看首页有啥新推荐", "image": "img/option/option/201612151145542KMA8ER1j4SuOhvo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 140580, "content": "追根溯源型，喜欢一个App，会把这个公司开发的App都下载下来", "image": "img/option/option/20161215152444NkneBd6bOaRQgLZh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 140582, "content": "断舍离型，会定期删除大量的App", "image": "img/option/option/20161206161948fDvdEym40L2qMe8g.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 140583, "content": "独辟蹊径型，关注各类小众的App推荐贴", "image": "img/option/option/201612201316356QG4zJdOTVcMSYmN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 140584, "content": "限免追踪型，经常关注应用市场的限时免费信息", "image": "img/option/option/20161215114350OEzrvoXuycGaMqBp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 140585, "content": "偶像包袱型，会把让自己觉